-- Alterra Wins Approval From Brazil Regulator to Start Reinsurer
-- B y   A n d r e a   L u d t k e
-- 2012-01-18T13:37:59Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-18/alterra-wins-approval-from-brazil-regulator-to-start-reinsurer.html
Alterra Capital Holdings Ltd. (ALTE) , the
firm formed by the merger of Max Capital Group Ltd. and
Harbor Point Ltd., said it won approval from Brazilian
regulators to establish a reinsurer in the country.  Alterra Resseguradora do Brasil SA will be located in  Rio
De Janeiro , according to a Business Wire statement today from
the Bermuda-based parent company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Andrea Ludtke in New York at 
 afrye@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Kraut at   dkraut2@bloomberg.net  